Chef solo starter pack

1. Start an EC2 instance running Ubuntu (I used Jaunty 9.04 Server from http://alestic.com/)

2. Bootstrap chef:
   $ rake bootstrap SERVER=ec2-XX-XX-XX-X.compute-X.amazonaws.com

3. Edit your cookbook.

4. Update:
   $ rake update SERVER=ec2-XX-XX-XX-X.compute-X.amazonaws.com

5. GOTO 3
